description: This file defines the WishlistItem class which models a wishlist item in a mobile app, including properties like id, userId, bookId, creation date, and optional book details. It also contains a factory constructor for creating instances from JSON data.

classes.name: WishlistItem
classes.description: A data model representing an item on a user's wishlist, including details like book title, author, and timestamps.

methods.name: WishlistItem.fromJson
methods.description: Factory constructor that creates a WishlistItem instance from a JSON map, parsing nested book details if available.
